### ================================================================
### Product Service - 내부 API 테스트 (order-service / company-service 호출 시뮬레이션)
### ================================================================

### [1] 상품 단건 조회 (내부)
GET {{baseUrl}}/internal/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
X-Internal-Request: true

### ================================================================

### [2] 재고 차감 (order-service 주문 생성 시뮬레이션)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/internal/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/stock/decrease
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Request: true

{
  "quantity": 10
}

### [3] 재고 복원 (order-service 주문 취소 시뮬레이션)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/internal/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/stock/restore
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Request: true

{
  "quantity": 10
}

### ================================================================

### [4] 재고 차감 실패 - 재고 초과
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/internal/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/stock/decrease
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Request: true

{
  "quantity": 99999
}

### [5] 재고 차감 실패 - 음수 수량 (INVALID_STOCK_QUANTITY)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/internal/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/stock/decrease
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Request: true

{
  "quantity": -1
}

### [6] 내부 API 헤더 누락 (PRODUCT_003 접근 거부)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/internal/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/stock/decrease
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### ================================================================

### [7] 업체 소속 상품 일괄 삭제 (company-service 업체 삭제 시뮬레이션)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/internal/api/v1/products/company/{{companyId}}
X-Internal-Request: true
X-User-Id: {{masterId}}
